# Features and Interactions

This document outlines the key interactive features and third-party libraries used in the project.

## Core Interactivity (handled by [assets/js/main.js](mdc:assets/js/main.js)):

*   **Navigation Menu:** Responsive mobile menu with toggle and link-click-close functionality.
*   **Skills Section:** Accordion-style reveal for skill details.
*   **Qualification Section:** Tabbed interface to switch between Education and Work history.
*   **Services Section:** Modal pop-ups to display detailed service information.
*   **Scrollspy:** Highlights the active navigation link based on the current scroll position.
*   **Dynamic Header:** Header background changes on scroll.
*   **Scroll-to-Top Button:** Appears on scroll, allowing quick navigation to the top of the page.
*   **Dark/Light Theme:** User-selectable theme preference (dark or light mode) stored in `localStorage`.

## Third-Party Libraries & Assets:

*   **Swiper.js:** ([assets/js/swiper-bundle.min.js](mdc:assets/js/swiper-bundle.min.js) & [assets/css/swiper-bundle.min.css](mdc:assets/css/swiper-bundle.min.css))
    *   Used for the interactive carousels in the **Portfolio** section.
    *   Used for the interactive carousels in the **Testimonial** section.
*   **Unicons:** (Linked via CDN in [index.html](mdc:index.html))
    *   Provides a wide range of icons used throughout the website (navigation, section headers, buttons, etc.).
*   **Google Fonts:** (Imported in [assets/css/styles.css](mdc:assets/css/styles.css))
    *   Uses the 'Poppins' font family.

## Key User Interactions:

*   Clicking navigation links smoothly scrolls to the respective sections.
*   Hover effects on buttons and links.
*   Interactive Swiper carousels (drag, click arrows/pagination).
*   Theme can be changed by clicking the moon/sun icon in the header.
